---
syntax: bash
tags:
- taskwarrior
---

# General taskwarrior usage
task <filter> <command> [<args>]

# To list all projects
task proj

# To list all tasks in project "errands"
task proj:errands

# To list tasks in project "errands" that contain description "milk"
task proj:errands milk

# To list all tags
task tag

# To list tasks with tag 'finance'
task +finance

# To change the project to "mentoring" for task 42
task 42 mod proj:mentoring

# To mark task 42 as complete
task 42 done

# To undo most recent change
task undo



